Create EventManager builder

Create 'math' package

Fix multiple 'javax.annotation.xa' definition
Idk why 'jboss-transaction-api' has it.

Create Vector2Type class
It maps MySQL point columns to Vector2 objects

Regenerate entities
Regenerate entities to match the current database structure. Also deleted the md5 files.

Initialize speedment
Initialize speedment by instantiating all available entity managers.

Finish speedment integration
So far, the integration with speedment is finished. The `Database` class holds the CRUD methods. The `KalaazuApplication` class is the database model and contains the managers for all the tables.

Create `delete` and `all` methods
The `delete` method deletes a single entity. The `all` method returns all entities.

Create module facade
Create the `Persistence` facade and the `PersistenceBuilder` builder.

Create event system
Created the classes for interacting with the event system module.

Move entities
The entities interfaces are now located in the `entities` package.
